    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进入地下赛车世界，拯救你的兄弟！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场激烈的街头竞速之旅中，你必须参加 <i>超级街机赛车</i> 锦标赛，才能找到你的兄弟，并揭开绑架他的神秘组织背后的真相。挑战重重，但只有胜利才能让你们再次团聚！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/c5462ae7b8fbd63ff1e43c95c686f7ef.webp?t=1738151528\" width=620 height=51 /></span><br><strong>🔥 热血剧情模式 🔥</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在扣人心弦的故事之中，跨越 <strong>5 大独特赛区</strong>，在 <strong>60 多条赛道</strong> 上疾驰，为了拯救兄弟一路狂飙！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/1be06a9d29454de9e9b0352fb91c2dc6.poster.avif?t=1738151528\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/1be06a9d29454de9e9b0352fb91c2dc6.webm?t=1738151528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/1be06a9d29454de9e9b0352fb91c2dc6.mp4?t=1738151528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/19f0d7dd7bd57c2a6b4fa960e33cb8db.webp?t=1738151528\" width=620 height=51 /></span><br><strong>🚗 无限个性化改装 🚗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义你的赛车造型和颜色，超过 <strong>十亿种</strong> 组合方式，让你的座驾独一无二！同时，不断升级赛车性能，让你在赛场上始终快人一步！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/9c3eb94ca2a0508ba7a063a9d47cfd1a.poster.avif?t=1738151528\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/9c3eb94ca2a0508ba7a063a9d47cfd1a.webm?t=1738151528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/9c3eb94ca2a0508ba7a063a9d47cfd1a.mp4?t=1738151528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/f79e4d38c615548d34b76f734163e370.webp?t=1738151528\" width=620 height=51 /></span><br><strong>🌍 线上 &amp; 本地多人对战 🌍</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跨平台在线对战</strong>——在专属服务器上，与全球玩家一较高下！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本地多人模式</strong>——支持最多 <strong>4 名玩家</strong> 同屏竞速，体验激情对决！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/e5060596acb5ced459032a2b253b1527.poster.avif?t=1738151528\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/e5060596acb5ced459032a2b253b1527.webm?t=1738151528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/e5060596acb5ced459032a2b253b1527.mp4?t=1738151528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/c6efd39a8af071830a8fd843d9f0e8ce.webp?t=1738151528\" width=620 height=51 /></span><br><br><strong>🏆 排行榜争霸 🏆</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲刺全球最快圈速，争夺排行榜巅峰荣耀！在 <strong>练习模式</strong> 中挑战自己的幽灵车，不断刷新个人纪录，向极限发起挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好加入<i>超级街机赛车</i>的世界了吗？现在就踏上这场狂野竞速之旅！🔥💨<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/1ce778a7fdb1aa6c5a919402a5f882ac.poster.avif?t=1738151528\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/1ce778a7fdb1aa6c5a919402a5f882ac.webm?t=1738151528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1103770/extras/1ce778a7fdb1aa6c5a919402a5f882ac.mp4?t=1738151528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
